        <br/>
        If you are looking for an e-commerce consultant, plugin builder or general know-it-all: Look no further, and
        contact me.
    </div>
{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
    <div class="bg-blue-400 font-extralight py-32 px-4" id="plugins">
        <div class="container mx-auto">
            <h3 class="text-blue-900 text-4xl font-display font-normal mt-10">My plugins</h3>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5 mt-8 pb-8">
                <a class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-105 flex flex-row items-center bg-white transition"
                   href="https://store.shopware.com/en/laene34427173466/cms-bootstrap-grid-section.html"
                   target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noopener">
                    <img src="./img/plugin/grid.png" alt="Grid plugin" class="w-1/3"/>
                    <div class="flex flex-col flex-1 px-5">
                        <strong class="text-gray-900 text-sm font-medium">CMS Bootstrap grid section</strong>
                        <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm font-medium">Customizable grid section that allows you to create your own custom grid. 1 sidebar is clearly not enough, so we built this plugin so you can customize your own grid.</span>
                    </div>
                </a>
                <a class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-105 flex flex-row items-center bg-white transition"
                   href="https://store.shopware.com/en/laene89843170115/digital-publishing-advanced-banners.html"
                   target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                    <img src="./img/plugin/publishing.png" alt="Publishing plugin" class="w-1/3"/>
                    <div class="flex flex-col flex-1 px-5">
                        <strong class="text-gray-900 text-sm font-medium">Digital Publishing</strong>
                        <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm font-medium">Create & manage responsive Digital Publishing banners from the Admin of your Shopware 6 shop. Use multiple layers with text, images, links, ... to create the banner</span>
                    </div>
                </a>
                <a class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-105 flex flex-row items-center bg-white transition"
                   href="https://store.shopware.com/en/laene69387022474/prism-code-editor.html"
                   target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                    <img src="./img/plugin/prism.png" alt="Prism Code Editor plugin" class="w-1/3"/>
                    <div class="flex flex-col flex-1 px-5">
                        <strong class="text-gray-900 text-sm font-medium">Prism Code Editor</strong>
                        <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm font-medium">Write custom html, css and javascript as a CMS Element in the Shopware page editor and create the pages of your dreams. Custom elements, images and more are now possible.</span>
                    </div>
                </a>
                <a class="relative rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-105 flex flex-row items-center bg-white transition"
                   href="https://store.shopware.com/en/laene77372187825/loyalty-program.html"
                   target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                    <img src="./img/plugin/loyalty.png" alt="Loyalty program plugin" class="w-1/3"/>
                    <div class="absolute bottom-3 left-3 bg-blue-900 text-blue-200 rounded-full px-2 text-xs">coming soon</div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col flex-1 px-5">
                        <strong class="text-gray-900 text-sm font-medium">Loyalty program</strong>
                        <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm font-medium">Create a unique loyalty program to reward your customers with exclusive discount campaigns. Use the flexible no-code Shopware Flow Builder to reward your customers with Loyalty Points.</span>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="text-right mt-3">
                <a href="https://store.shopware.com/en/laenen.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
                   class="bg-blue-900 hover:bg-black transition text-blue-200 hover:text-white rounded-full py-4 px-5 text-sm font-bold uppercase">Find
                    me on the Shopware Store</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-violet-400 font-extralight py-32 px-4" id="services">
        <div class="container mx-auto">
            <h3 class="text-violet-900 text-4xl font-display font-normal mt-10">My services</h3>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5 mt-8 text-violet-900">
                <div class="bg-violet-300 rounded-lg p-4 shadow-lg">
                    <b>Shopware 6 development</b><br/>
                    Want your own Shopware plugin? Or do you have a problem that you can't fix? Want to launch a new
                    webshop? Contact me, and let's see how I can help you and your business.
                </div>
                <div class="bg-violet-300 rounded-lg p-4 shadow-lg">
                    <b>Graphical design</b><br/>
                    In need of stationary? Flyers? Posters? Web-banners? Let's talk and see what I can do.
                </div>
                <div class="bg-violet-300 rounded-lg p-4 shadow-lg">
                    <b>Shopware 6 audit</b><br/>
                    Slow website? Bad SEO? I offer auditing services. I don't run some cheap tools on your website, but
                    really dive into the source code to find out what could be wrong on your webshop.<br/>
                    Bad code, missing dependencies, slow integrations: I will find it all.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center mt-10 text-3xl">
                Interested? Contact me: <a href="mailto:rune@laenen.me" class="no-underline hover:underline hover:decoration-violet-800 hover:decoration-wavy">rune@laenen.me</a>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="bg-rose-400 font-extralight py-32 px-4" id="blog">
        <div class="container mx-auto">
            <h3 class="text-rose-900 text-4xl font-display font-normal mt-10">My blogposts</h3>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5 mt-8 text-rose-900">
                {% for slug, blogPost in blogPosts %}
                    <a href="{{ path('app_blog_blogpost', {slug}) }}" {% if blogPost.type == 'external' %}target="_blank" rel="noopener"{% endif %} class="flex flex-col relative bg-rose-200 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-center transition hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-105">
                        <img src="{{ blogPost.cover.image }}" alt="{{ blogPost.cover.alt }}" class="rounded-t-lg" loading="lazy" />
                        <div class="p-4 flex flex-1 justify-center items-center">
                            <b>{{ blogPost.title }}</b><br />
                        </div>
                        <div class="absolute top-3 right-3">
                            <div class="inline-block p-2 rounded-full z-50 bg-rose-900 text-rose-300 text-xs">
                                {{ blogPost.date|date("d/m/Y") }}
                            </div>
                            {% if blogPost.type == 'external' %}
                                <div class="inline-block p-2 rounded-full z-50 mt-1 bg-rose-900 text-rose-300 text-xs">
                                    Guest blog
                                </div>
                            {% endif %}
                            {% if blogPost.language is defined %}
                                <div class="inline-block p-2 rounded-full z-50 mt-1 bg-rose-900 text-rose-300 text-xs">
                                    {{ blogPost.language }}
                                </div>
                            {% endif %}
                        </div>
                    </a>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
{% endblock %}
